modName: Sporty Sexy Map - Athletic muscle mod CBBE UNP UNPB ADEC
summary: Sporty Sexy Map is a normal map which will create a well trained body for your favorite female character. No massive bulky women with veins poppin' of their chests. Just some nice definition to create a sexy toned body.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://static-2.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/13377-1-1356542731.jpg[/img]

Sporty Sexy Map is an normal map mod which will create a athletic well-trained body for your favorite female character. No massive bulky women with veins poppin' of their chests. Just some nice definition to create a sexy toned body. Swinging around swords and axes builds up some muscle definition after all!

Sporty Sexy Map is available for CBBE v3, Dimonized UNP & UNP Skinny, ADEC and Vanilla (Skyrim default) body meshes.

[s]August 28th 2012,
Hi everybody,
Please take the time to read this short message from the author of this mod.

I would really like to thank you all for downloading and rating my mod. I have enjoyed every screenshot which used my mod, whether it was mentioned or not. I have never thought this mod would be as popular as it is and I smile when I think about it.

Currently I'm reaching 1000 endorsements and that seems like a good time to call it a day and keep everything as it is.

Unless the freshly announced DLC Heartfire will bring something completely new to the table (which it probably will not), I won't do any updates on this mod.

To be honest, I haven't played the game in months now. I really want to but my double jobs are getting in the way :)

Anyway, I'll check in from time to time to see if there are any questions. Private messages are still forwarded to my email so don't hesitate contacting me if you have any (non-idiot) questions. Have a good one and I'm really glad I was able to improve your Skyrim immersion.

Cheers to all!

XS2Reality
[/s]

Installation
=======================================
Install through NNM or unpack the contents to the Data folder

When using a Race mod - The Ashen, Temptress etc
=======================================
1) Determine which body is used by the race mod (UNP, CBBE, ADEC, Vanilla)
2) Manually download the correct file and extract the file 'femalebody_1_msn.dds'
3) Place the file in the texture directory of the mod (the mods often use separate texture files)

Examples:
Ashen: SkyrimdatatexturesactorscharacterOrientalfemale
Temptress: SkyrimDatatexturestemptressactorscharacterfemale


File contents / Uninstallation
=======================================
SkyrimDatatexturesactorscharacterfemalefemalebody_1_msn.dds




Notes
=======================================
- Sporty Sexy Map use the same seams as the original normal maps and should not extra seams.
- Overwrites only the existing normal (muscle) map
- Does NOT affect the body texture or glossiness of the model

Comptibility with body mods
=======================================
Dimonized UNP Body mesh / UNP Blessed use "Sporty UNP" (2 versions available)
Dimonized UNP Skinny Body mesh uses "Sporty UNP skinny - Athletic muscle map - Symmetrical Abs"
Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition CBBE / CBBEv3m use "Sporty CBBE"
Acdale EyeCandy Body ADEC uses "Sporty ADEC"
Standard skyrim body mesh users use "Sporty Vanilla"


FAQ
=======================================
Q: Do you also have a complete skin?
A: Not for now, but there is a many compatible skins available on the Nexus. One excellent skin is made for UNPB and has an adaptation of Sporty Sexy Map Included, have a look at [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24318]Barbarian and Milkdrinker Skin UNP and UNPB by HoneyVanity[/url]

Q: I want more defined abs, arms, legs!!
A: Sporty Map is made to create an athletic body and not a body builder type. You can refer to [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=44]Tigersan's

Female Muscle Mod[/url] or [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3218]Shootme's CBBE v1_02 muscle mod[/url]

Q: How do I get it to look (glossy) like in the screenshots?
A: The screenshots are the result of a combination of mods of the main are [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24828]Unbleak ENB[/url] and a custom specular / gloss map. The spec map will be released as Sporty Sexy Sweat in the very near future.

Q: Can you make this for Khajit or Argonian?
A: Unfortunately I don't have the time nor the interest to work on anthropomorphic characters. You're free to use the assets though...

Q: Can you make X changes for me?
A: I definitely don't have the time to cater all requests. You're free to use the assets though...

Q: I am highly offended / disgusted / confused / sexually confused by this mod! / Why would you create such sexist and homoerotic mod?
A: One of the visual founders of modern fantasy lore - and inspiration to the Skyrim developers - is Boris Vallejo. This mod is in homage to his art work - bulky men and athletic women. Google it and be amazed or disgusted, in any case. Talk about 'the Lore' and you talk about Boris Vallejo.

Q: I am the creator of a a complete new body mesh, can you help me with my texturing and normal maps?
A: Please send me some screenshots of the model. If I like the body mesh I will definitely make time for you.

Q: Why is this file soooo big, I'm getting CTD's over here!
A: All DXT compression methods used in Skyrim have pretty heavy compression artifacts. The used compression in this file is 8.8.8 RGB which is lossless. If you have crashes you can try a texture compressor (also available on the Nexus). In my opinion it's better to reduce the image size to 1024 with no compression than 2048 with heavy compression...

Q: What the heck is a normal map?
A: Normal mapping can be explained as a 3-channel type bump mapping. The normal map gives a low poly meshe more detail - in our case; the muscle definition.
